quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  94,1,Have We not opened your heart for you (O Muhammad)
  94,2,and removed your burden from you
  94,3,which weighed down your back
  94,4,and raised high for you your fame
  94,5,"Surely, with the hardship, there is relief"
  94,6,"Surely, with the hardship, there is relief"
  94,7,"When you have finished (your work), then stand up (for Allah’s worship)"
  94,8,and turn (your attention) to your Lord